0width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Workforce%20Innovation%20Series%3A%20Chris-Deri%20on%20light%20blue%20background%20with%20grid%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b0f834b4912df3ae18ea8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChris%20Deri.%3Cp%3EWeber%20Shandwick%20Collective%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChris%20Deri%20leads%20Weber%20Shandwick's%20corporate-advisory%20business%20and%20is%20on%20BI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkforce-innovation-board-tackles-topics-such-as-c-suite-innovation-ai-worker-wellness-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorkforce%20Innovation%20board%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20an%20advisor%20to%20execs%2C%20he%20finds%20navigating%20the%20most%20pressing%20workplace%20issues%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fworkforce-innovation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorkforce%20Innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20the%20forces%20shaping%20enterprise%20transformation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20%26quot%3BWorkforce%20Innovation%26quot%3B%20series%20is%20gathering%20perspectives%20from%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20industry%20verticals%20and%20corporate%20roles%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20drivers%20of%20change%20in%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%2C%20worker%20well-being%2C%20and%20C-suite%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Deri%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Weber%20Shandwick%20Collective's%20corporate-advisory%20business%2C%20advises%20chief%20communications%20officers%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officers%2C%20and%20other%20C-suite%20executives%20on%20policy%2C%20governance%2C%20crisis%20management%2C%20and%20other%20management%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20conducted%20by%20the%20firm%2C%20Deri%20said%2C%20found%20CEOs%20were%20prioritizing%20AI%2C%20even%20if%20they%20didn't%20yet%20know%20how%20to%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20year%2C%20we%20asked%20CEOs%2C%20'What%20is%20the%20action%20you%20plan%20to%20take%20this%20year%20with%20regards%20to%20AI%3F'%26quot%3B%20Deri%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20cited%20action%20was%2C%20'Secure%20an%20AI%20and%20technology%20vendor.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20AI%20really%20occupying%20the%20minds%20of%20business%20leaders%20as%20much%20as%20we%20think%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20everybody%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20is%20on%20the%20radar%20and%20a%20priority.%20We%20did%20research%20on%20CEOs%20and%20other%20C-suite%20executives%20about%20the%20four%20megatrends%20that%20we%20see%20impacting%20business%20%E2%80%94%20generative%20AI%2C%20green%20transition%2C%20geopolitics%2C%20and%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20interesting%20across%20all%20of%20those%2C%20and%20generative%20AI%20in%20particular%2C%20was%20executives%20expressed%20limited%20personal%20confidence%20in%20their%20own%20ability%20to%20lead%20their%20organizations%20through%20these%20transformations.%20Only%2013%25%20of%20the%20executives%20that%20we%20spoke%20to%20felt%20they%20were%20very%20capable%20of%20leading%20their%20own%20organization%20through%20the%20AI%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20low%20level%20of%20confidence%20among%20executives%20about%20their%20own%20organization's%20ability%20to%20reskill%20their%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20incredible%20amount%20of%20hype%20and%20speculation%20in%20the%20ecosystem%20and%20in%20the%20media.%20But%20I%20feel%20like%20executives%20are%20taking%20a%20kind%20of%20walk-before-they-run%20perspective%2C%20and%20I%20sense%20a%20lot%20of%20caution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20leadership%20qualities%20are%20needed%20to%20manage%20the%20pace%20of%20innovation%20today%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20we%20think%20about%20in%20terms%20of%20technology%2C%20of%20AI%20in%20particular%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20is%20probably%20true%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20things%3A%20Executives%20need%20to%20be%20hands-on%2C%20and%20they%20need%20to%20be%20taking%20on%20the%20ethos%20of%20technologists.%20They%20should%20have%20caution%2C%20but%20they%20should%20adopt%20some%20of%20the%20principles%20in%20the%20technology%20world%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20test%20and%20learn%2C%20and%20we're%20going%20to%20fail%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20time%20when%20you%20can%20guarantee%20results.%20You%20can%20try%20things%20out%20in%20a%20way%20that%20protects%20IT%20systems%2C%20but%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20different%20ethos%20than%20many%20executives%20have%2C%20which%20is%20to%20have%20already%20looked%20around%20the%20corner%20to%20see%20what's%20there.%20We%20just%20all%20are%20not%20in%20that%20place.%20This%20is%20an%20era%20of%20complexity%2C%20and%20we%20really%20got%20to%20embrace%20the%20complexity%20and%20the%20open-ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20are%20you%20advising%20companies%20to%20handle%20the%20polarization%20and%20politicization%20of%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDEI%20and%20ESG%20have%20been%20hijacked%20by%20our%20politically%20polarized%20times.%20From%20a%20communication%20standpoint%2C%20we%20often%20advise%20our%20clients%20not%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20outside%20noise%20and%20to%20make%20decisions%20about%20these%20things%20based%20on%20data%20and%20what's%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20the%20enterprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20analysis%20to%20track%20discussions%20and%20the%20stakeholder%20groups%20driving%20the%20whole%20%26quot%3Bantiwoke%26quot%3B%20movement.%20There%20are%20people%20who%20subscribe%20to%20antiwoke-ism%2C%20but%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20the%20size%2C%20velocity%2C%20and%20volume%20of%20the%20antiwoke%20movement%20online%20have%20been%20conflated%2C%20mostly%20because%20the%20movement%20is%20just%20highly%20engaged.%20There's%20not%20necessarily%20a%20corollary%2C%20just%20the%20sheer%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20happens%20is%20that%20these%20online%20conversations%20jump%20to%20the%20mainstream%20media%2C%20and%20they%20get%20reported%20as%20megamovements.%20We're%20using%20AI-backed%20analytics%20to%20track%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20people%20who%20have%20passionate%20views%20about%20DEI%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20but%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20reasons%2C%20we%20really%20try%20to%20advise%20our%20clients%20not%20to%20focus%20as%20much%20on%20those%20discussions%20because%20they%20can%20become%20an%20incredible%20distraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20return-to-office%20mandates%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20tricky%20issue%20for%20many%20companies%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERedefining%20workplace%20well-being%20and%20employee-company%20contracts%20post-COVID%20is%20still%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%20In%20a%20hundred%20years%2C%20historians%20will%20tell%20us%20what%20this%20phase%20was%20about%2C%20but%20it%20really%20feels%20like%20we%20are%20still%20figuring%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20concerned%20that%20the%20hybrid%20nature%20of%20work%2C%20and%20the%20still-work-in-progress%20of%20defining%20the%20hybrid%20nature%20of%20work%2C%20is%20hurting%20us%20from%20a%20learning%20standpoint%20and%20a%20culture%20standpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20are%20also%20confused%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20workplace%20messaging.%20When%20you%20look%20at%20the%20CEOs%20who%20get%20the%20most%20attention%2C%20whether%20it's%20Amazon's%20or%20Jamie%20Dimon%2C%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20really%20black%20and%20white%20about%20it%20are%20the%20exceptions.%20Everybody%20else%20is%20really%20loosey-goosey%20about%20the%20messaging.%20A%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20everybody%20was%20petrified%20that%20if%20you%20enforced%20any%20kind%20of%20return%20to%20office%2C%20people%20would%20jump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20think%20that%20the%20lifestyles%20of%20even%20senior%20executive%20decision-makers%20have%20changed%20with%20hybrid%20work%2C%20and%20that%20influences%20some%20of%20the%20policies%20that%20they%20institute%20across%20an%20entire%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20a%20concrete%20example%20of%20how%20you%20are%20integrating%20AI%20into%20your%20workplace%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20mundane%2C%20but%20it's%20had%20the%20most%20impact.%20We%20just%20had%20training%20for%20a%20few%20hundred%20folks%20in%20the%20corporate-advisory%20business.%20We%20were%20talking%20about%20how%20to%20use%20generative%20AI%20to%20do%20what%20we%20call%20%26quot%3Bred%20teaming%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20basically%20a%20way%20to%20test%20ideas%2C%20concepts%2C%20and%20messaging%20with%20AI%20personas%20of%20different%20stakeholders%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20senator%2C%20an%20investor%2C%20or%20a%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20them%20through%20the%20technical%20aspects%20of%20how%20to%20do%20that.%20We%20talked%20about%20proper%20prompting.%20But%20what%20we%20needed%20to%20get%20across%20to%20them%20is%20that%20this%20is%20not%20to%20outsource%20to%20AI%20the%20work%20that%20you%20do%20as%20a%20practitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20is%20to%20enhance%20it%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20to%20accelerate%20things.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20to%20hand%20over%20your%20duties%20as%20a%20thinker%20and%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20knowledge%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20our%20case%2C%20as%20an%20advisor%20to%20your%20clients%20who%20understands%20the%20business%20%E2%