a%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpadel-vs-pickleball-the-future-of-racket-sports-in-america-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EPadel%20has%20gained%20steam%20this%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20a%20more%20active%20alternative%20to%20the%20widely%20popular%20pickleball%2C%20writes%20Business%20Insider's%20Kathleen%20Elkins%2C%20who's%20already%20been%20won%20over.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOften%20described%20as%20a%20mix%20between%20tennis%20and%20squash%2C%20padel%20is%20played%20on%20a%20court%20smaller%20than%20tennis%20but%20bigger%20than%20pickleball.%20It's%20also%20surrounded%20by%20four%20glass%20walls%20with%20two%20openings%2C%20allowing%20players%20to%20chase%20shots%20outside%20the%20enclosure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20larger%20court%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20play%20balls%20off%20or%20outside%20the%20four%20walls%20mean%20the%20game%20requires%20a%20higher%20level%20of%20athleticism%20than%20the%20more%20stationary%20pickleball.%20(Settle%20down%2C%20pickleballers.%20Your%20game%20requires%20quicker%20reflexes.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20you%20might%20have%20heard%20of%20padel%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20you've%20never%20seen%20a%20court%20in%20person.%20The%20sport%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpadel-isnt-just-rich-people-pickleball-heres-the-difference-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Edominated%20by%20the%20ultrawealthy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Some%20elite%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpadel-courts-miami-new-york-luxury-real-estate-development-amenity-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Ebuilt%20courts%20in%20their%20backyards%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20catching%20the%20padel%20bug.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E