internships%20aimed%20at%20improving%20employability%20and%20research%20skills%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntegration%20of%20Workshop%20with%20Workplace%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EInternships%20should%20align%20classroom%20or%20lab%20learning%20with%20workplace%20outcomes%2C%20integrating%20experiences%20from%20various%20settings%20such%20as%20enterprises%2C%20start-ups%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20research%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20the%20World%20of%20Work%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Internships%20offer%20students%20a%20chance%20to%20grasp%20the%20challenges%20and%20opportunities%20of%20the%20workplace%2C%20helping%20them%20align%20their%20expectations%20and%20behaviour%20with%20industry%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHybrid%20Model%20Learning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBy%20combining%20physical%20and%20digital%20learning%20modes%2C%20internships%20can%20broaden%20learning%20opportunities%2C%20especially%20when%20blended%20with%20mentorship%20from%20industry%20or%20research%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeveloping%20Research%20Aptitude%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EInternships%20should%20provide%20conditions%20for%20students%20to%20sharpen%20their%20research%20skills%2C%20familiarise%20themselves%20with%20analytical%20tools%2C%20and%20understand%20research%20methodologies%2C%20data%20analysis%2C%20and%20ethical%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExposure%20to%20Emerging%20Technologies%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Interns%20should%20be%20exposed%20to%20new%20technologies%20that%20can%20enhance%20work%20processes%2C%20including%20traditional%20fields%20like%20art%2C%20craft%2C%20and%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnhancing%20Entrepreneurial%20Capabilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Internships%20should%20help%20students%20understand%20how%20organisations%20are%20formed%2C%20encouraging%20them%20to%20develop%20entrepreneurial%20skills%20and%20consider%20starting%20their%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3