c.gov.in%2Fpdfnews%2F2051511_Internship-Research-Internship-Guidelines.pdf%5C%22%3EUGC's%20Guidelines%20for%20Internship%2FResearch%20Internships%20For%20Undergraduate%20Students%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternship%20Mechanism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20internship%20process%20is%20structured%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHigher%20Education%20Institutions%20(HEIs)%20will%20identify%20Internship%20Providing%20Organisations%20(IPOs).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIPOs%20will%20post%20internship%20opportunities%20on%20a%20designated%20portal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudents%20will%20request%20internships%20through%20their%20HEI's%20Nodal%20Officer.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Nodal%20Officer%20will%20endorse%20and%20upload%20student%20requests%20to%20the%20portal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIPOs%20will%20select%20interns%20based%20on%20their%20criteria.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInternship%20supervisors%20will%20evaluate%20and%20follow%20up%20on%20the%20internship%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInterns%20will%20submit%20a%20final%20report%20upon%20completion%20of%20the%20internship.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC%20emphasises%20that%20structured%20internships%20are%20vital%20for%20improving%20graduates'%20employability%20and%20research%20skills%2C%20helping%20them%20transition%20smoothly%20into%20the%20workforce%20or%20academic%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724678040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ffn9rvt1o_internship-_625x300_26_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fexplained-internship-mechanism-designed-for-undergraduate-students-6422488%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Internships%20offer%20students%20a%20chance%20to%20grasp%20the%20challenges%20and%20opportunities%20of%20the%20workplace%2C%20helping%20them%20align%20their%20expectations%20and%20behaviour%20with%20industry%20demands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Schoolgirl%20Punched%2C%20Kicked%20By%20A%20Group%20Of%20Girls%20In%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20girls%20kicked%2C%20punched%2C%20elbowed%20and%20dragged%20a%20school%20girl%20by%20her%20hair%20following%20an%20argument%2C%20showed%20a%20disturbing%20video%20from%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%2C%20which%20happened%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20was%20reported%20from%20Yari%20Road%20locality%20in%20Versova.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disturbing%20video%2C%20filled%20with%20expletives%2C%20shows%20a%20bunch%20of%20girls%20punching%20a%20girl%2C%20in%20a%20school%20dress%2C%20mercilessly%20even%20as%20she%20falls%20to%20the%20ground.%20The%20attackers%20and%20the%20victim%20are%20all%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20gets%20up%2C%20clutches%20her%20head%20and%20walks%20over%20to%20her%20friend.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20one%20of%20the%20attackers%20shouts%20%26quot%3Bidhar%20aa%2C%20idhar%20aa%20(Come%20here%2C%20come%20here)%2C%20and%20follows%20it%20up%20with%20an%20expletive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20intervenes.%20Some%20people%20riding%20their%20scooters%20stop%20and%20watch%20the%20proceedings.%20A%20gas%20cylinder%20delivery%20man%2C%20stops%20his%20cycle%20and%20watches%20from%20afar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPaani%20main%20dal%20(Throw%20her%20in%20the%20water)%26quot%3B%2C%20shouted%20another.%20They%20all%20gang%20up%20again%20and%20pull%20her%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20it%20is%20punches%20and%20kicks%20all%20over%20again%2C%20shows%20the%20video.%20The%20victim%20is%20violently%20pulled%20around.%20An%20attacker%20climbs%20on%20her%20back%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20video%2C%20and%20starts%20punching%20her%20furiously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20boy%20gets%20in%20and%20pulls%20the%20girl%20up%20and%20tells%20her%20to%20go%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounselling%20of%20all%20girls%20and%20their%20parents%20was%20done%20by%20Versova%20Police%20Station%20officials%20and%20Sneha%20Foundation%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee.%20The%20concerned%20school%20principals%20are%20also%20informed%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20investigating%20who%20circulated%20the%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20messages%20on%20X%2C%20the%20police%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTaking%20cognisance%20of%20a%20viral%20video%20of%20the%20attack%20on%20a%20girl%20in%20Versova%2C%20Nirbhaya%20squad%20(special%20cell%20to%20prevent%20crime%20against%20women%2Fchildren)%20conducted%20an%20investigation.%20During%20the%20investigation%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20all%20the%20girls%20visible%20in%20the%20video%20are%20minors%20and%20belong%20to%20the%20same%20locality.%20An%20argument%20over%20a%20small%20issue%20led%20to%20a%20fight%20between%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nirbhaya%20squad%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20matter%20and%20patrolling%20has%20been%20increased%20at%20the%20location%2C%20said%20the%20police.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724677920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fmjp9pm48_schoolgirl-attacked_625x300_26_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-schoolgirl-punched-kicked-by-a-group-of-girls-in-mumbai-6422482%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20group%20of%20girls%20kicked%2C%20punched%2C%20elbowed%20and%20dragged%20a%20school%20girl%20by%20her%20hair%20following%20an%20argument%2C%20showed%20a%20disturbing%20video%20from%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20US'%20New%20Missile%20Will%20Be%20A%20Game-Changer%20In%20Indo-Pacific%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20deployed%20its%20new%20long-range%20air-to-air%20missile%20that%20could%20potentially%20disrupt%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20in%20the%20US-China%20'Cold%20War'.%20The%20AIM-174B%20missile%2C%20onboard%20the%20US%20Navy's%20F-18%20Super%20Hornet%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20many%20pictures%2C%20is%20known%20to%20have%20an%20operational%20range%20of%20approximately%20400%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIM-174B%20derivative%20of%20the%20Raytheon%20SM-6%20surface-to-air%20missile%20operated%20out%20of%20US%20naval%20platforms.%20The%20SM-6%20is%20a%20multi-role%20missile%20used%20for%20anti-air%20warfare%2C%20anti-ballistic%20missiles%2C%20and%20anti-surface%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fj3fpu9q_aim174b-missile_625x300_26_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIM-174B%20was%20reportedly%20first%20spotted%20during%20the%20Rim%20of%20the%20Pacific%20(RIMPAC)%20exercise%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20naval%20exercise%20with%2026%20participants.%20The%20missile%20was%20attached%20to%20a%20hardpoint%20under%20the%20wings%20of%20the%20Super%20Hornet%2C%20garnering%20attention%20due%20to%20its%20potential%20to%20disrupt%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20About%20AIM-17B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20Interceptor%20Missile%20(AIM)-174B%20is%20the%20air-to-air%20version%20of%20the%20SM-6%20missile.%20It%20is%20readily%20available%20due%20to%20the%20existing%20production%20line%20for%20the%20SM-6%20missile.%20The%20Raytheon%20SM-6%20missile%20has%20a%20booster%20stage%2C%20which%20propels%20the%20missile%20into%20the%20air%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20solid%20rocket%20booster%20and%20sustainer%20motor%20of%20the%20missile%20work%20to%20hit%20the%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SM-6%20weighs%20around%201%2C500%20kilograms%2C%20while%20the%20AIM-174%20weighs%20approximately%20850%20kg%20due%20to%20no%20booster%20motor.%20The%20US%20Navy's%20new%20missile%20has%20a%20speed%20of%20Mach%203.5%2C%20i.e.%203.5%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20sound.%20The%20missile%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20direct%20equivalent%20of%20the%20Russian%20Rh-37%20Vympel%20long-range%20hypersonic%20air-to-air%20missile%20with%20a%20range%20of%20400%20km%20and%20the%20Chinese%20PL-15%20long-range%20missile%20has%20a%20range%20of%20300-350%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20SM-6%20missile%20is%20three%20missiles%20in%20one%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20SM-6%20missile%20is%20three%20missiles%20in%20one%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvf4u7vu8_sm6-missile-_625x300_26_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SM-6%20missile%20is%20three%20missiles%20in%20one%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Image%20credit%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rtx.com%2Fraytheon%2Fwhat-we-do%2Fsea%2Fsm-6-missile%5C%22%3Ewww.rtx.com%2Fraytheon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20PLA%20Navy%20has%20reportedly%20deployed%20an%20advanced%20version%20of%20PL-15%2C%20the%20PL-17%20missile%2C%20with%20a%20range%20of%20400%20km.%20The%20last%20dedicated%20long-range%20air-to-air%20missile%20the%20US%20Navy%20had%20was%20the%20AIM-54%20Phoenix%20for%20the%20F-14%20Tomcat.%20The%20fighter%20jet%20and%20the%20missile%20were%20out%20of%20service%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20the%20US%20Navy's%20doctrine%20used%20long-range%20AIM-54%20Phoenix%20to%20defeat%20Russian%20air%20threats%20before%20they%20could%20come%20closer%20to%20carrier%20battle%20groups.%20After%20the%20USSR%20broke%20up%20and%20the%20Russian%20Navy's%20strength%20fell%2C%20the%20US%20Navy%20stopped%20investing%20in%20such%20missiles%20and%20retired%20the%20AIM-54%20Phoenix.%20Today%2C%20the%20development%20of%20the%20AIM-174B%20over%2030%20years%20after%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20broke%20proves%20the%20US%20Navy%20is%20once%20again%20returning%20to%20its%20Cold%20War%20naval%20doctrine%2C%20with%20China%20replacing%20Russia%20as%20the%20main%20maritime%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20air-to-air%20missiles%20in%20the%20age%20of%20stealth%20fighters%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20China%20are%20extensively%20building%20new%20generation%20stealth%20fighter%20jets%20that%20can%20evade%20enemy%20radars%20by%20going%20undetected%20and%20striking%20inside%20their%20territory.%20The%20US%20began%20with%20the%20F-117%20Nighthawk%20fighter%20bomber%2C%20then%20the%20F-22%20Raptor%20and%20now%20the%20F-35%2C%20the%20most%20advanced%20fighter%20jet%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20not%20behind%20with%20its%20Chengdu%20J-20%20fifth-generation%20stealth%20fighter%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20stealth%20fighters%20can%20avoid%20detection%2C%20then%20why%20are%20nations%20focusing%20on%20long-range%20air-to-air%20missiles%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20fear.%20China%20developed%20the%20PL-15%20long-range%20missile%2C%20which%20can%20be%20deployed%20on%20the%20J-20%2C%20meaning%2C%20now%20a%20stealth%20fighter%20can%20strike%20targets%20from%20far%20away%20without%20getting%20detected.%20Recently%2C%20the%20PL-17%20was%20deployed%20on%20its%20J-16%20fourth-generation%20fighter.%20China's%20move%20shifted%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20in%20the%20air%20in%20the%20volatile%20region%20of%20East%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22P-15%20is%20reportedly%20capable%20of%20destroying%20targets%20at%20a%20distance%20of%20300km%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22P-15%20is%20reportedly%20capable%20of%20destroying%20targets%20at%20a%20distance%20of%20300km%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fojeek7i8_pl15-missile_625x300_26_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP-15%20is%20reportedly%20capable%20of%20destroying%20targets%20at%20a%20distance%20of%20300km%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpremium.globalsecurity.org%2Fmilitary%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fpl-15.htm%5C%22%3Epremium.globalsecurity.org%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20stealthy%20Chinese%20aircraft%20could%20theoretically%20spot%20non-stealthy%20U.S.%20aircraft%20and%20shoot%20them%20down%20well%20outside%20the%20range%20where%20they%20could%20even%20fight%20back%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-navys-newest-air-to-air-missile-could-tilt-balance-in-south-china-sea-6336606%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20quoting%20Kelly%20Grieco%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Stimson%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20US%20stealth%20aircraft%20might%20be%20forced%20to%20fly%20dangerously%20close%20to%20fire%20their%20missiles.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20Chinese%20fighter%20can%20outrange%20an%20American%20fighter%2C%20it%20means%20they%20can%20get%20the%20first%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20outrun%20something%20that's%20travelling%20at%20Mach%204.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIM-174B%20was%20quickly%20developed%20to%20address%20this%20need.%20Now%2C%20US%20fighter%20jets%20can%20target%20Chinese%20military%20installations%20from%20long%20range%2C%20avoiding%20the%20danger%20of%20flying%20close%20to%20the%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustin%20Bronk%2C%20an%20airpower%20and%20technology%20expert%20at%20London's%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%2C%20told%20Reuters%20that%20China%20is%20developing%20long-range%20missiles%2C%20but%20the%20radar%20of%20launching%20aircraft%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20spot%20targets%20at%20such%20distances.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20go%20too%20big%20and%20too%20heavy%20on%20missiles%2C%20then%20you%20end%20up%20trading%20off%20fuel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Airborne%20Warning%20and%20Control%20(AWAC)%20aircraft%20acts%20as%20an%20aerial%20command%20centre%20during%20combat%2C%20and%20combat%20patrol%20missions.%20These%20aircraft%20detect%20the%20enemy%20from%20long%20range.%20The%20new%20missiles%20will%20be%20tasked%20to%20strike%20high-value%20targets%20like%20the%20AWACs%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Island%20Chains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20potential%20direct%20military%20face-off%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20could%20happen%20near%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieendowment.org%2Fposts%2F2015%2F07%2Famericas-security-role-in-the-south-china-sea%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Sea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20major%20transit%20route%20for%20maritime%20trade%20and%20the%20US%20Navy.%20China%20has%20threatened%20Taiwan%20with%20a%20military%20invasion%20and%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20full-blown%20Chinese%20assault%2C%20the%20US%20is%20bound%20by%20law%20to%20defend%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Taiwan%20Relations%20Act%20mandates%20that%20the%20US%20have%20a%20policy%20to%20provide%20Taiwan%20with%20arms%20of%20a%20defensive%20character%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Foreign%20Policy%20statesman%20John%20Foster%20Dulles%20presented%20the%20Island%20Chain%20Strategy%20to%20keep%20a%20check%20on%20USSR%20and%20Chinese%20expansion%20by%20establishing%20military%20bases%20on%20the%20West%20Pacific.%20The%20USSR%20collapsed%20in%201991%2C%20but%20the%20Chinese%20economic%20and%20military%20expansion%20made%20the%20strategy%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20works%20on%20several%20lines%20of%20defence%20for%20the%20US%20to%20stop%20any%20military%20invasion.%20The%20strategy%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20World%20War%20II%20when%20Imperial%20Japan%20took%20over%20most%20of%20East%20Asia%20and%20attacked%20Pearl%20Harbour%2C%20effectively%20bringing%20the%20US%20to%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20military%20conflict%20around%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20will%20fall%20within%20the%20First%20Island%20Chain%2C%20which%20comprises%20the%20Kuril%20Island%2C%20claimed%20by%20Japan%20but%20under%20Russian%20control%2C%20the%20Japanese%20archipelago%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20the%20north%20Philippines%2C%20and%20Borneo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20First%20Island%20Chain%20is%20an%20important%20geopolitically%20important%20boundary%20for%20the%20US%20area%20with%20vast%20amounts%20of%20natural%20resources%20and%20economic%20significance.%20Any%20conflict%20would%20mean%20the%20US%20operating%20close%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20First%20Island%20Chain%20is%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defence%20for%20the%20US%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20First%20Island%20Chain%20is%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defence%20for%20the%20US%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fdjs875lo_first-island-chain_625x300_26_August_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20First%20Island%20Chain%20is%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defence%20for%20the%20US%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.960cyber.afrc.af.mil%2F%5C%22%3Ewww.960cyber.afrc.af.mil%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20would%20come%20even%20closer%20to%20China%20if%20Beijing%20invaded%20Taiwan.%20An%20AIM-174B%20missile%20would%20keep%20its%20aircraft%20carriers%20and%20fighter%20jets%20at%20a%20safer%20distance%20and%20put%20PLA%20hunting%20ships%20and%20aircraft%20carriers%20out%20of%20range.%20Reuters%20reported%20quoting%20a%20Taiwan-based%20strategist%20that%20this%20would%20increase%20the%20likelihood%20of%20the%20US%20directly%20getting%20involved%20in%20a%20military%20conflict%20with%20China%20over%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20game-changer%20missile%20would%20push%20the%20US%20further%20into%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20region%20therefore%20titling%20the%20equation%2C%20which%20as%20of%20now%20remains%20in%20China's%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20And%20Its%20Air-to-Air%20Missile%20Arsenal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20developed%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no%20follow%2C%20no%20index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drdo.gov.in%2Fdrdo%2Ftechnology-cluster-links%2Flabs-products-detail%2F2093%2F182%5C%22%3E%20Astra%20Mk1%3C%2Fa%3E%20beyond%20visual%20range%20air-to-air%20missile%20that%20is%20operational%20and%20mounted%20on%20the%20Su-30MKI%20fighter%20jet.%20The%20Astra%20Mk1%20has%20a%20speed%20of%20Mach%204.5%20with%20a%20range%20of%20100%20kilometres.%20The%20Astra%20Mk2%20and%20Mk3%20are%20under%20trial%20but%20are%20far%20behind%20what%20the%20US%20and%20China%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20extremely%20long-range%20BVR%20missiles%20is%20based%20on%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20or%20Indian%20Navy%20unlike%20the%20US%20and%20China.%20The%20Astra%20Mk1%20is%20operational%20on%20Su-30MKI%20so%20at%20present%20only%20the%20IAF%20operates%20the%20missile%20but%20later%20it%20will%20be%20developed%20for%20other%20aircraft%20too.%20The%20primary%20long-range%20air-to-air%20missile%20in%20service%20with%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20is%20the%20Meteor%20on%20the%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%2C%20which%20is%20widely%20considered%20the%20most%20advanced%20air-to-air%20missile%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724677680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fjrahrc9o_aim174b-missile_625x300_14_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-how-us-new-missile-will-be-a-game-changer-in-indo-pacific-6421399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20has%20deploy