flammatory%20comments.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20Kangana's%20department%20to%20speak%20on%20farmers%2C%20Kangana's%20statement%20is%20personal.%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20farmer-friendly.%20The%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20working%20against%20us%20and%20Kangana's%20statement%20is%20doing%20the%20same.%20She%20should%20not%20make%20such%20statements%2C%20on%20sensitive%20or%20religious%20issues%2C%20religious%20organisations%2C%26quot%3B%20Punjab%20BJP%20leader%20Harjit%20Grewal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20comments%20also%20drew%20a%20response%20from%20the%20Congress%20with%20leader%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20asking%20the%20BJP%20leader%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20well%20soon%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Surjewalal%2C%20who%20is%20campaigning%20in%20poll-bound%20Haryana%20that%20witnessed%20year-long%20farmers'%20protest%2C%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWere%20these%20just%20Kangana's%20words%20or%20did%20someone%20else%20copy%20them%3F%20If%20not%2C%20then%20why%20is%20the%20BJP%20silent%20on%20the%20issue%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Ranaut%2C%20known%20for%20her%20provocative%20remarks%2C%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20critic%20of%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20against%20the%20now-repealed%20three%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20she%20allegedly%20misidentified%20a%20woman%20farmer%20from%20Punjab%20who%20was%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20protests%20and%20called%20her%20Bilkis%20Bano%20-%20an%20elderly%20woman%20who%20had%20become%20one%20of%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20anti-Citizenship%20Amendment%20Law%20(CAA)%20protests%20earlier%20in%20Delhi's%20Shaheen%20Bagh.%20She%20had%20also%20said%20the%20woman%20was%20%26quot%3Bavailable%20for%20Rs%20100%26quot%3B%2C%20suggesting%20she%20could%20be%20hired%20for%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%20that%20resurfaced%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranaut-slapped-kangana-ranaut-slapgate-spotlights-her-controversial-2020