0a%20gathering%20after%20unveiling%20a%20statue%20in%20Agra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20of%20playing%20divisive%20politics%20yesterday%2C%20saying%20they%20are%20more%20concerned%20about%20votebank%20than%20the%20plight%20of%20Hindus%20in%20the%20Bangladesh%20after%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20post%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20left%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20opposition%20is%20quick%20to%20speak%20out%20on%20global%20issues%2C%20it%20has%20remained%20conspicuously%20silent%20about%20the%20persecution%20of%20Hindus%20and%20the%20demolition%20of%20temples%20in%20Bangladesh.%20They%20see%20Palestine%20but%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20Bangladesh%20because%20its%20fears%20losing%20their%20vote%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20unite%20to%20expose%20and%20counter%20those%20divisive%20forces%20that%20seek%20to%20fracture%20society%20for%20their%20petty%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20today%2C%20he%20encapsulated%20a%20veiled%20warning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20work%20for%20unity.%20We%20will%20not%20allow%20anyone%20any%20scope%20of%20spreading%20divisiveness%20in%20society%2C%20be%20it%20in%20the%20name%20of%20case%2C%20region%2C%20language%2C%20or%20an%20any%20other%20ground.%20We%20should%20be%20wary%20of%20such%20people%20and%20we%20should%20do%20our%20duty%20as%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724672820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fs6e90fko_yogi-adityanath_625x300_26_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbatenge-toh-katenge-yogi-adityanath-makes-strong-pitch-for-unity-6421793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20citing%20the%20case%20of%20neighbouring%20Bangladesh%2C%20has%20made%20a%20strong%20pitch%20for%20national%20unity%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3B%20Batenge%20toh%20katenge%20(If%20we%20are%20divided%2C%20we%20will%20be%20destroyed).%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbatenge-toh-katenge-yogi-adityanath-makes-strong-pitch-for-unity-6421793%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%20On%20Why%20It's%20Advantage%20Congress%20In%20Haryana%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20set%20to%20sweep%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Haryana%2C%20veteran%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20today.%20On%20whether%20he%20will%20be%20Chief%20Minister%20again%2C%20the%20senior%20leader%20said%20the%20Congress%20has%20a%20detailed%20process%20to%20decide%20such%20matters%20and%20that%20the%20high%20command%20takes%20the%20call%20after%20talks%20with%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20he%20is%20so%20confident%20of%20a%20Congress%20victory%20in%20the%20October%201%20election%2C%20Mr%20Hooda%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20the%20signs%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20people%20have%20made%20up%20their%20mind%20that%20a%20Congress%20government%20would%20be%20formed.%20We%20did%20not%20win%20any%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20seat%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20This%20time%2C%20we%20won%20five%20and%20our%20vote%20share%20went%20up%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%20was%20asked%20why%20he%20is%20so%20confident%20of%20a%20Congress%20sweep%20because%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20won%20five%20seats%20each%20in%20the%202024%20general%20election.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20won%20five%20seats%2C%20but%20we%20lost%20in%20many%20places%20with%20a%20slim%20margin%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20is%20the%20Congress's%20advantage%20in%20this%20election%2C%20Mr%20Hooda%20pointed%20to%20the%20work%20under%20his%20government%20before%202014.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20left%20the%20government%20in%202014%2C%20Haryana%20was%20ahead%20in%20per%20capita%20income%2C%20law%20and%20order%2C%20employment%20and%20in%20sports.%20These%20are%20not%20my%20figures%2C%20these%20are%20Planning%20Commission's%20figures.%20And%20where%20have%20we%20reached%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years.%20Haryana%20in%20now%20unsafe%2C%20our%20wrestler%20daughters%20have%20to%20sit%20in%20protest%20for%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20agitation%20by%20the%20country's%20top%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Sakshee%20Malikkh%2C%20over%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20wrestling%20boss%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20Congress%20leaders%20said%2036%20'biradari'%20--%20a%20phrase%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20all%20castes%20and%20communities%20in%20Haryana%20--%20are%20behind%20the%20Congress%20in%20this%20election.%20%26quot%3BLast%20time%2C%20the%20people%20gave%20us%20the%20responsibility%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20Opposition%20and%20we%20raised%20their%20voice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20BJP's%20claims%20of%20development%2C%20he%20said%20unemployment%20has%20tripled%20under%20their%20rule.%20%26quot%3BThey%20saw%20they%20will%20increase%20incomes.%20That%20did%20not%20happen%20but%20expenses%20tripled.%20Every%20section%20is%20worried%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hooda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20the%20ruling%20party%20over%20its%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20against%20him%2C%20Mr%20Hooda%20said%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20set%20up%20to%20probe%20the%20charges%20is%20yet%20to%20submit%20its%20report.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20list%20so%20many%20scams%20by%20them.%20They%20can%20only%20level%20allegations.%20But%20the%20people%20have%20decided%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Congress%20preps%20for%20the%20big%20fight%2C%20many%20see%20infighting%20as%20a%20big%20obstacle%20in%20the%20party's%20road%20to%20a%20good%20poll%20show.%20Posters%20of%20Congress%20MP%20Kumari%20Selja%20--%20considered%20an%20arch-rival%20of%20Mr%20Hooda%20--%20have%20come%20up%20and%20she%20has%20said%20she%20wants%20to%20contest%20the%20state%20polls.%20Asked%20about%20the%20infighting%20angle%2C%20Mr%20Hooda%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20infighting%20in%20Congress.%20We%20are%20a%20democratic%20organisation.%20There%20can%20be%20a%20difference%20of%20opinions.%20When%20the%20party%20decides%2C%20everyone%20unites.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20urged%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20briefly%20postpone%20the%20October%201%20polls%2C%20citing%20holidays%20before%20and%20after%20the%20election%20date.%20Commenting%20on%20this%2C%20Mr%20Hooda%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Haryana%20are%20smart.%20They%20won't%20waste%20their%20votes%20because%20of%20holidays.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20also%20responded%20to%20the%20BJP's%20allegations%20of%20dynasty%20politics%20against%20him.%20Mr%20Hooda's%20son%20Deepender%20Singh%20Hooda%20is%20a%20five-time%20Congress%20MP.%20%26quot%3BMy%20grandfather%20and%20father%20were%20freedom%20fighters.%20I%20have%20served%20the%20people%20and%20Deepender%20has%20done%20the%20same.%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20my%20family%20that%20we%20are%20serving%20the%20people%20for%20four%20generations.%20This%20is%20democracy.%20Only%20those%20who%20serve%20move%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20AAP%20contesting%20the%20polls%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20division%20of%20votes%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20alliance%20we%20had%20was%20at%20the%20national%20levels.%20We%20have%20not%20spoken%20to%20them.%20Here%20the%20fight%20is%20between%20BJP%20and%20Congress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20polls%20will%20also%20be%20a%20test%20for%20the%20Dushyant%20Chautala-led%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%2C%20which%20pulled%20up%20a%20stunner%20by%20winning%2010%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20state%20polls%20and%20went%20on%20to%20join%20the%20BJP-led%20ruling%20alliance.%20The%20alliance%20with%20BJP%20over%2C%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20has%20now%20said%20JJP%20may%20join%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20if%20it%20gets%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hooda%2C%20however%2C%20ruled%20out%20any%20such%20plan.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20is%20capable%20and%20we%20do%20not%20need%20it.%20We%20have%20not%20spoken%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20many%20seats%20he%20expects%20Congress%20to%20win%2C%20the%20veteran%20leader%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20talk%20about%20numbers%2C%20but%20I%20can%20say%20the%20Congress%20will%20form%20the%20government%20with%20a%20significant%20majority.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724672460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fubeo5508_bhupinder-hooda_625x300_26_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-election-bhupinder-hooda-exclusive-bhupinder-hooda-on-why-its-advantage-congress-in-haryana-polls-6421739%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20is%20set%20to%20sweep%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Haryana%2C%20veteran%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-election-bhupinder-hooda-exclusive-bhupinder-hooda-on-why-its-advantage-congress-in-haryana-polls-6421739%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22KPI%20Green%20Energy%20receives%20LoIs%20for%2013.30%20MW%20green%20energy