%20after%20the%20JDS-BJP%20alliance%2C%20claimed%20%26quot%3Bstar%20treatment%20for%20criminals%26quot%3B%20lodged%20at%20the%20Parappana%20Agrahara%20Jail%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20talked%20about%20for%20years%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20issue%20is%20not%20new.%20It%20happened%20in%20the%20past%20too%20(and)%20led%20to%20a%20huge%20issue%20between%20senior%20police%20officers...%20there%20was%20a%20fight%20over%20demands%20for%20investigation.%20Now%20they%20are%20talking%20of%20criminals%20being%20shifted.%20We%20need%20to%20see%20what%20they%20(the%20Congress%20government)%20will%20do...%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20will%20people%20believe%20this%20government%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20law%20and%20order%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20-%20already%20under%20fire%20and%20facing%20prosecution%20in%20the%20alleged%20Mysuru%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20scam%20case%20-%20has%20vowed%20to%20take%20action%20against%20erring%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F7-prison-officials-suspended-over-special-treatment-for-actor-darshan-in-jail-6419353%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E7%20Prison%20Officials%20Suspended%20Over%20VIP%20Treatment%20For%20Actor%20Darshan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20prison%20staffers%20have%20been%20suspended%20so%20far.%20%26quot%3BFurther%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20others%20as%20well.%20I%20have%20directed%20the%20Home%20Minister%20(G%20Parameshwara)%20to%20visit%20the%20prison%20and%20conduct%20an%20investigation...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decision%20will%20also%20be%20taken%20on%20transferring%20Darshan%20Thoogudeepa%20to%20another%20jail%2C%20his%20office%20said%20today%2C%20adding%20Karnataka%20Police%20chief%20Alok%20Mohan%20had%20been%20told%20to%20submit%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20and%2013%20others%20are%20in%20Parappana%20Agrahara%20Central%20Jail%20over%20the%20horrific%20murder%20of%20Renukaswamy%2C%20who%20was%20allegedly%20kidnapped%2C%20tortured%2C%20and%20murdered%20by%20the%20actor's%20accomplices%20after%20he%20apparently%20sent%20obscene%20messages%20to%20actress%20Pavithra%20Gowda%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20Darshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenukaswamy's%20body%20was%20found%20in%20stormwater%20drain%20on%20June%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20others%20accused%20in%20this%20case%20are%20in%20another%20prison%20in%20Tumakuru%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20Treatment%20For%20Murder-Accused%20Actor%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photo%20that%20has%20sparked%20this%20flood%20of%20attacks%20on%20the%20Congress%20shows%20Darshan%20and%20three%20other%20men%20relaxing%20in%20plastic%20chairs%20on%20a%20small%20law.%20The%20actor%20is%20seen%20smiling%20and%20holding%20a%20coffee%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkannada-actor-darshan-viral-jail-pic-special-treatment-for-murder-accused-actor-in-jail-viral-pic-sparks-row-6416340%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpecial%20Treatment%20For%20Murder%20Accused%20Actor%20In%20Jail%3F%20Pic%20Sparks%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20have%20said%20the%20others%20in%20the%20convivial%20scene%20are%20his%20manager%20and%20co-accused%20Wilson%20Garden%20Naga%20and%20Kulla%20Seena%2C%20also%20an%20inmate%20at%20the%20prison.%20Footage%20from%20a%20video%20call%20showing%20Darshan%20speaking%20to%20an%20as%20yet%20unknown%20person%20has%20also%20been%20widely%20circulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20cannot%20independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20image%20or%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-viral-jail-photo-clip-showing-kan