0on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F1au7jk3g_hema-_625x300_26_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20actor%20and%20producer%20Siddique%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20as%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Malayalam%20Movie%20Artistes%20(AMMA).%20Within%20hours%2C%20noted%20Malayalam%20filmmaker%20Ranjith%20stepped%20down%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20Kerala%20Chalachitra%20Academy.%20Both%20men%20resigned%20amid%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20assault%20which%20came%20up%20against%20them%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20explosive%20revelations%20of%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20Report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20290-page%20report%2C%20released%20last%20week%2C%20exposes%20the%20rampant%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20women%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%2C%20as%20also%20their%20terrible%20working%20conditions.%20It%20details%20the%20impunity%20with%20which%20the%20industry's%20overwhelmingly%20male%20power%20structure%20exploits%20women%20actors%20and%20others%2C%20secure%20in%20the%20knowledge%20that%20the%20victims%20will%20not%20dare%20to%20complain%20or%20protest%20for%20fear%20of%20reprisals.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20activists%20are%20jubilant%20that%20in%20this%20iniquitous%20and%20toxic%20ecosystem%2C%20two%20influential%20men%20suddenly%20found%20themselves%20publicly%20accused%20of%20sexual%20misconduct%2C%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20had%20to%20step%20down%20from%20their%20lofty%20positions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20Another%20Blip%20In%20History%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20damning%20as%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20Report%20is%2C%20will%20it%20lead%20to%20substantive%20changes%20within%20the%20Kerala%20film%20industry%20so%20women%20who%20work%20in%20it%20are%20not%20coerced%20into%20providing%20sexual%20favours%20to%20the%20powers-that-be%2C%20nor%20treated%20like%20second-class%20citizens%20without%20access%20to%20equal%20rights%3F%20Or%20will%20the%20findings%20get%20buried%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20institutional%20apathy%2C%20and%20reforms%2C%20if%20any%2C%20simply%20fail%20to%20get%20off%20the%20ground%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trajectory%20of%20the%20report%20itself%20does%20not%20seem%20encouraging.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20set%20up%20a%20three-member%20committee%20headed%20by%20Justice%20K.%20Hema%20to%20examine%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20women%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry.%20The%20move%20came%20after%20a%20leading%20actress%20in%20the%20industry%20was%20sexually%20assaulted%20in%20a%20moving%20car%2C%20allegedly%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20a%20prominent%20actor.%20Soon%20after%20this%2C%20a%20group%20of%20women%20from%20the%20industry%20came%20together%20to%20form%20the%20Women%20in%20Cinema%20Collective%20(WCC).%20It%20was%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20this%20group%20that%20the%20state%20government%20took%20the%20initiative%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKerala%20Government's%20Questionable%20Actions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20from%20there%20on%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government's%20conduct%20became%20perplexing%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20The%20panel%2C%20which%20interviewed%20a%20large%20number%20of%20men%20and%20women%20from%20the%20industry%2C%20including%20actors%2C%20directors%2C%20producers%2C%20scriptwriters%2C%20make-up%20artists%20and%20so%20on%2C%20was%20ready%20with%20its%20report%20as%20early%20as%20December%202019.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20refused%20to%20publish%20it%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20contained%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%20information''%20and%20could%20violate%20the%20privacy%20of%20certain%20individuals.%20It%20is%20only%20now%2C%20almost%20five%20years%20later%2C%20that%20a%20court%20order%20has%20ensured%20the%20report's%20release%2C%20albeit%20with%20several%20redacted%20portions%20to%20protect%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20alleged%20perpetrators%20and%20victims%20of%20sexual%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20look%20at%20the%20salient%20features%20of%20the%20report%20and%20you%20know%20that%20several%20people%20must%20have%20been%20extremely%20keen%20to%20keep%20it%20under%20wraps.%20The%20picture%20that%20emerges%20from%20it%20is%20that%20of%20a%20film%20industry%20controlled%20by%20a%20cabal%20of%20powerful%20male%20actors%2C%20directors%20and%20producers%20who%20routinely%20subject%20women%20-%20be%20they%20actors%2C%20technicians%20or%20other%20professionals%20-%20to%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20exploitation.%20They%20are%20told%20to%20%26quot%3Badjust%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcompromise'%2C%20euphemisms%20for%20agreeing%20to%20provide%20sex%20when%20demanded.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20entire%20industry%20seems%20to%20be%20actuated%20by%20an%20odious%20patriarchal%20belief%20that%20if%20a%20woman%20has%20chosen%20to%20make%20a%20career%20in%20show%20business%2C%20she%20is%20sexually%20available.%20And%20if%20she%20hopes%20to%20succeed%2C%20she%20had%20better%20be%20ready%20to%20sexually%20indulge%20those%20who%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20give%20her%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20also%20found%20that%20the%20women%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20poorly%20paid%20and%20often%20denied%20contractual%20safeguards.%20The%20junior%20artists%2C%20especially%2C%20are%20treated%20like%20slaves%2C%20says%20the%20report%2C%20and%20not%20provided%20with%20basic%20facilities%20like%20toilets%20and%20changing%20rooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESilent%2C%20Fearful%2C%20Cowed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20barely%20a%20word%20is%20spoken%20against%20this%20systemic%20culture%20of%20abuse.%20If%20a%20woman%20does%20raise%20her%20voice%20against%20the%20injustice%20and%20the%20relentless%20sexual%20harassment%20that%20goes%20on%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%2C%20she%20finds%20work%20drying%20up%20and%20is%20viciously%20trolled%20on%20social%20media.%20The%20intimidation%20can%20be%20so%20extreme%20that%20she%20may%20even%20fear%20for%20her%20life.%20Naturally%2C%20this%20ensures%20that%20most%20women%20in%20the%20industry%20remain%20silent%2C%20fearful%20and%20cowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20grim%20exposure%2C%20and%20despite%20the%20public%20outcry%20against%20it%2C%20the%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20government%20initially%20refused%20to%20take%20suo%20motu%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators%20whose%20names%20have%20come%20up%20in%20the%20report.%20Instead%2C%20it%20said%20that%20it%20would%20initiate%20proceedings%20against%20the%20individuals%20if%20and%20when%20a%20woman%20lodges%20a%20formal%20complaint%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20problematic%20decision%2C%20since%20most%20women%20in%20this%20country%20are%20reluctant%20to%20go%20public%20with%20complaints%20of%20sexual%20abuse.%20However%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20political%20storm%20that%20has%20erupted%20following%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20report%20and%20criticism%20that%20it%20was%20trying%20to%20protect%20certain%20important%20men%2C%20late%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20government%20set%20up%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20to%20probe%20the%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20The%20Report%20Not%20Be%20So%20Easy%20To%20Ignore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20certainly%20a%20start.%20But%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20SIT's%20findings%20translate%20into%20some%20concrete%20action%20on%20the%20ground.%20When%20the%20%23MeToo%20movement%20was%20tearing%20through%20India%20back%20in%202018%2C%20several%20prominent%20men%2C%20including%20Bollywood%20actors%20such%20as%20Nana%20Patekar%2C%20Alok%20Nath%20and%20others%2C%20were%20called%20out%20as%20sexual%20predators.%20Nothing%20much%20came%20of%20those%20charges%20eventually.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20Report%20ought%20to%20be%20much%20harder%20to%20sweep%20under%20the%20carpet%2C%20since%20it%20is%20an%20exhaustive%20and%20meticulous%20expos%C3%A9%3B%20of%20the%20pervasive%20culture%20of%20economic%20discrimination%20and%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20women%20in%20an%20entire%20industry.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20report%20offers%20a%20real%20opportunity%20to%20not%20just%20hold%20the%20guilty%20to%20account%2C%20but%20also%20to%20put%20in%20place%20laws%2C%20structures%2C%20and%20safeguards%20to%20make%20the%20industry%20a%20safe%2C%20humane%20and%20gender-just%20workplace%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20the%20government%20of%20Kerala%20rise%20to%20the%20challenge%3F%20Or%20will%20it%20merely%20pay%20lip%20service%20and%20wait%20to%20ride%20out%20the%20storm%2C%20so%20everyone%20can%20go%20back%20to%20business%20as%20usual%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shuma%20Raha%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20author)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724669880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqluebti_hema_625x300_26_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhema-committee-report-can-kerala-government-rise-above-lip-service-6421476%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Damning%20as%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20Report%20is%2C%20will%20it%20lead%20to%20substantive%20changes%20within%20the%20Kerala%20film%20industry%20so%20women%20who%20work%20in%20it%20are%20not%20coerced%20into%20providing%20sexual%20favours%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhema-committee-report-can-kerala-government-rise-above-lip-service-6421476%22%2C%2