arp%20response%20to%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20after%20she%20highlighted%20incidents%20of%20rape%20across%20India%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20now%20flagged%20that%20Bengal%20has%20been%20allocated%20123%20fast-track%20courts%20to%20hear%20cases%20of%20rapes%20and%20child%20abuse%2C%20but%20many%20of%20them%20are%20not%20functional%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20fire%20after%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20in%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20shot%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20last%20week%2C%20demanding%20a%20tough%20central%20law%20to%20punish%20rapists.%20The%20Trinamool%20supremo%20highlighted%20in%20her%20letter%20that%2C%20according%20to%20available%20data%2C%2090%20rape%20cases%20occur%20in%20the%20country%20daily.%20And%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20victims%20are%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20horrifying%20to%20see%20this%20trend.%20It%20shakes%20the%20confidence%20and%20conscience%20of%20society%20and%20the%20nation.%20It%20is%20our%20bounden%20duty%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20it%20so%20that%20women%20feel%20safe%20and%20secure.%20Such%20a%20serious%20and%20sensitive%20issue%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed%20comprehensively%20through%20stringent%20central%20legislation%20that%20prescribes%20exemplary%20punishment%20for%20those%20involved%20in%20these%20dastardly%20crimes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%2C%20also%20proposing%20establishment%20of%20fast-track%20special%20courts%20to%20tackle%20such%20cases.%20%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20quick%20justice%2C%20trials%20should%20preferably%20be%20completed%20within%2015%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnpurna%20Devi%2C%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%2C%20has%20now%20written%20to%20Ms%20Banerjee%20in%20response%20to%20her%20letter%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Ms%20Devi%20started%20by%20expressing%20her%20condolences%20to%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20doctor%20raped%20and%20murdered%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20minister%20then%20said%20that%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20implemented%20last%20month%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensively%20addresses%20the%20issues%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20by%20providing%20stringent%20punishments%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20fast%20track%20courts%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20a%20centrally%20sponsored%20scheme%20to%20set%20up%20such%20courts%20was%20launched%20in%20October%202019.%20%26quot%3BAs%20of%2030.06.2024%2C%20752%20FTSCs%20including%20409%20exclusive%20POCSO%20Courts%20are%20functional%20in%2030%20States%2FUTs%20which%20have%20disposed%20of%20more%20than%202%2C53%2C000%20cases%20since%20the%20inception%20of%20scheme.%20Under%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20State%20of%20West%20Bengal%20was%20allocated%20a%20total%20of%20123%20FTSCs%2C%20which%20included%2020%20exclusive%20POCSO%20Courts%20and%20103%20combined%20FTSCs%20dealing%20with%20both%20rape%20and%20POCSO%20Act%20cases.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20these%20courts%20had%20been%20operationalized%20till%20mid-June%2C%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20State%20of%20West%20Bengal%20communicated%20its%20willingness%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Scheme%20vide%20letter%20dated%2008.06.2023%2C%20committing%20to%20start%207%20FTSCs.%20Under%20the%20revised%20target%2C%20West%20Bengal%20has%20been%20allocated%2017%20FTSCs%2C%20of%20which%20only%206%20exclusive%20POCSO%20Courts%20have%20been%20operationalized%20as%20of%2030.06%202024.%20In%20spite%20of%20a%20pendency%20of%2048%2C600%20rape%20and%20POCSO%20cases%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20State%20Government%20has%20not%20taken%20any%20steps%20to%20start%20the%20remaining%2011%20FTSCS.%20Action%20in%20this%20regard%20is%20pending%20with%20the%20state%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Minister%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20has%20not%20implemented%20a%20national%20helpline%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Centre%20to%20respond%20to%20distress%20calls%20from%20women%20or%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecognizing%20the%20need%20for%20Helplines%20as%20first%20responders%20in%20the%20golden%20hour%20to%20a%20woman%20or%20child%20in%20distress%2C%20Women%20Helpline%20(WHL)%20181%2C%20Emergency%20Response%20Support%20System%20(ERSS)%20-112%2C%20Child%20Helpline%201098%2C%20Cyber%20Crime%20Helpline%20-%201930%20have%20been%20put%20in%20place%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20The%20WHL%20and%20Child%20Helplines%20have%20been%20integrated%20with%20ERSS%20also.%20But%2C%20unfortunately%20the%20people%20of%20the%20State%20of%20West%20Bengal%20cannot%20utilize%20this%20facility%20as%20the%20State%20Government%20has%20not%20implemented%20the%20WHL%20despite%20many%20requests%20and%20reminders%20from%20Gol%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20minister%20said%20the%20existing%20legal%20framework%20is%20stringent%20enough%20to%20tackle%20the%20crimes%20against%20women.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20you%20would%20agree%20that%20effective%20implementation%20of%20these%20provisions%20of%20law%20as%20well%20as%20various%20initiatives%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20for%20women's%20safety%20falls%20in%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20State%20Government.%20It%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20State%20machinery%20is%20fully%20sensitised%20and%20geared%20up%20to%20take%20fullest%20advantage%20of%20the%20legal%20and%20schematic%20provisions%20made%20by%20the%20Central%20Government%20for%20ensuring%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20in%20the%20State%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20sincerely%20hope%20and%20trust%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20West%20Bengal%20will%20strive%20towards%20eliminating%20all%20forms%20of%20discrimination%20and%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20girls%20by%20creating%20a%20safe%20and%20secure%20ecosystem%20and%20gender%20equal%20society%20for%20them%20to%20grow%20and%20prosper%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724669700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fhjuvb57g_mamata-banerjee_625x300_23_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F123-fast-track-courts-centre-responds-after-mamata-banerjee-flags-rapes-6420927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20now%20flagged%20that%20Bengal%20has%20been%20allocated%20123%20fast-track%20courts%20to%20hear%20cases%20of%20rapes%20and%20child%20abuse%2C%20but%20none%20of%20these%20are%20functional.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F123-fast-track-courts-centre-responds-after-mamata-banerjee-flags-rapes-6420927%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infosys%20shares%20update%20on%20onboarding%20delays%3A%20%E2%80%98Everyone%20with%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724669526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112806360%2Cimgsize-20702.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Finfosys-ceo-salil-parekh-shares-important-update-on-onboarding-delays-everyone-with%2Farticleshow%2F112806168.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infosys%20CEO%20Salil%20Parekh%20has%20assured%20that%20offers%20made%20to%20freshers%20would%20be%20honored%20and%20joining%20would%20commence%20despite%20some%20date%20changes.%20This%20statement%20followed%20reports%20and%20a%20complaint%20by%20NITES%20about%20delayed%20onboarding%20of%202%2C000%20engineering%20graduates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Finfosys-ceo-salil-par