lters%20include%20options%20like%20salary%20information%2C%20years%20of%20experience%20required%2C%20and%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20AI%2C%20the%20assumption%20was%20that%20employers%20have%20to%20give%20the%20input%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mir%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20have%20to%20actually%20come%20in%20and%20post%20jobs%20and%20even%20if%20things%20are%20fully%20automated%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20you%20still%20have%20these%20human%20touch%20points%20who%20are%20creating%20these%20job%20posts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMir%20and%20Nilforoshan%20looked%20at%20ChatGPT%20and%20realized%20that%20this%20human%20involvement%20wasn't%20strictly%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20a%20human%20to%20tell%20you%20what%20the%20salary%20range%2C%20job%20type%2C%20and%20job%20function%20are.%20You%20can%20actually%20just%20extract%20and%20infer%20all%20that%20information%20using%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Nilforoshan%2C%20scrapping%20listings%20by%20employers%2C%20recruiters%20and%20offshore%20agencies%20has%20resulted%20in%20higher%20quality%20openings%2C%20as%20he%20said%20this%20move%20has%20minimized%20the%20risk%20of%20spam%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-posting-fake-job-listings-search-resume-2024-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHaller%2520said%2520employers%2520that%2520dangle%2Cout%2520they%2520were%2520being%2520hoodwinked.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efake%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20randomized%20positions%2C%20and%20untrustworthy%20data%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231235be7-0876-4c3d-9ea2-2fcf726497f8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20personal%20motivation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20explained%20that%20both%20have%20a%20personal%20motivation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapplied-hundreds-jobs-struggling-get-hired-bridge-job-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20improve%20the%20search%20e