apartment-rent-price-setting-landlords-realpage-lawsuit-illegal-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BTypically%2C%20that's%20the%20telltale%20sign%20of%20collusion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20RealPage%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225732%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kamala%20Harris%20speaking%20at%20a%20podium.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c0db865da406397bf6bd42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223821%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKamala%20Harris%20has%20centered%20her%20housing%20plan%20in%20her%20presidential%20campaign.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c30c51d6-8ab6-4c77-b091-71fff394c915%5C%22%3EAddressing%20the%20housing%20shortage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20targeting%20landlords%20using%20price-setting%20algorithms%2C%20Harris%20backed%20a%20piece%20of%20legislation%20designed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fny1.com%2Fnyc%2Fall-boroughs%2Fnews%2F2024%2F01%2F05%2Fhedge-fund-rental-housing-home-affordable-representative-adam-smith-congress-%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520End%2520Hedge%2520Fund%2520Control%2Cfrom%2520holding%2520those%2520properties%2520completely.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20crack%20down%20on%20Wall%20Street%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20buy%20homes%20in%20bulk.%20But%20these%20efforts%20would%20address%20the%20housing%20crisis%20only%20on%20the%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20rent-setting%20algorithms%20might%20be%20driving%20up%20prices%20in%20some%20markets%2C%20much%20bigger%20supply%20and%20demand%20forces%20are%20to%20blame%20for%20the%20broader%20affordability%20crisis.%20But%20it's%20politically%20popular%20to%20go%20after%20Wall%20Street%20investors%20and%20landlords%20engaged%20in%20predatory%20behaviors.%20Republican%20lawmakers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabc6onyourside.com%2Fon-your-side%2Fproblem-solvers%2Fohio-housing-crisis-state-federal-legislation-us-senators-jd-vance-sherrod-brown-stop-predatory-investing-act-institutional-investors-foreign-home-buyers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincluding%20JD%20Vance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20supported%20cracking%20down%20on%20investors%20buying%20up%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20sort%20of%20a%20belief%20that%20big%20landlords%20have%20more%20power%20than%20they%20actually%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Jenny%20Schuetz%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20urban%20economics%20and%20housing%20policy%20at%20the%20Brookings%20Institution%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20But%20she%20argued%20that%20trying%20to%20prevent%20these%20practices%20isn't%20a%20bad%20idea.%20%26quot%3BThe%20question%20is%20what%20do%20you%20do%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20and%20is%20there%20actually%20action%20that's%20going%20to%20help%20consumers%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20risk%20that%20regulating%20landlords%2C%20either%20in%20how%20they%20set%20rents%20or%20in%20which%20homes%20they%20purchase%2C%20could%20backfire%20by%20reducing%20investment%20in%20homes%20and%20thus%20hurting%20supply.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20actually%20cracked%20down%20really%20hard%20on%20private%20equity%2C%20it%20would%20be%20less%20capital%20going%20into%20this%20space%2C%20less%20capital%20going%20into%20investing%20in%20new%20homes%2C%26quot%3B%20Ben%20Metcalf%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Terner%20Center%20for%20Housing%20Innovation%20at%20UC%20Berkeley%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERedfin's%20chief%20economist%2C%20Daryl%20Fairweather%2C%20argued%20that%20Harris%20was%20prioritizing%20regulating%20predatory%20behavior%20by%20landlords%20as%20a%20way%20to%20appeal%20to%20first-time%20homebuyers%20and%20renters%20who%20feel%20taken%20advantage%20of%20and%20outcompeted%20in%20the%20market.%20It%20can