l.%20The%20panel%20has%20said%20that%20one%20person%20in%20the%20gathering%20was%20heard%20threatening%20the%20minor%20daughter%20of%20Mr%20Banerjee%20with%20rape%20and%20publicly%20announcing%20a%20reward%20of%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%20to%20anyone%20who%20commits%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20filthy%20intention%20of%20the%20miscreant%20and%20his%20indecent%20remark%20in%20public%20amounts%20to%20outraging%20the%20modesty%20of%20a%20minor%20girl%20and%20also%20endangering%20her%20safety%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commission%20has%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20called%20upon%20police%20to%20take%20action%20under%20the%20stringent%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%20and%20the%20UN%20Convention%20on%20Rights%20of%20a%20Child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20entire%20state%20is%20mourning%20the%20sad%20demise%20of%20the%20doctor%20at%20RG%20Kar%2C%20calling%20for%20another%20rape%20to%20settle%20scores%20is%20clearly%20violative%20of%20the%20law%20and%20could%20send%20out%20a%20dangerous%20message%20to%20society%20if%20punitive%20measures%20are%20not%20taken.%20This%20can%20put%20not%20just%20the%20minor%20girl%20in%20question%20but%20all%20minor%20girls%20at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20rights%20body%20has%20sought%20from%20the%20police%20an%20action%20taken%20report%20in%20this%20matter%20within%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Trinamool%20leader%20Derek%20O'Brien%20took%20to%20X%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BFight%20us%20politically%20with%20your%20filthy%20tricks.%20You%20have%20done%20it%20before.%20But%20today%20you%20have%20crossed%20the%20line.%20Stop%20threatening%20kids.%20No%20words%20enough%20to%20condemn%20the%20gutter%20level%20threats%20to%20our%20National%20General%20Secretary's%20daughter.%20STOP%20THIS%20NOW%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20and%20surrounding%20areas%20are%20witnessing%20massive%20protests%20over%20the%20chilling%20incident%20of%20rape-murder%20at%20the%20state-run%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%20The%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20state%20government%20and%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20are%20drawing%20fire%20for%20the%20handling%20of%20the%20matter.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20supremo%20has%20hit%20back%2C%20alleging%20a%20nexus%20between%20Opposition%20parties%20BJP%20and%20CPM%20of%20creating%20unrest%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%2C%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20sensitive%20case%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20CBI.%20Before%20the%20case%20transfer%2C%20Kolkata%20Police%20had%20arrested%20one%20accused%2C%20Sanjoy%20Roy.%20The%20CBI%20is%20yet%20to%20make%20any%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724663160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fieqmulh_abhishek-banerjee_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-rape-threat-to-abhishek-banerjees-daughter-bengal-child-panel-takes-note-6420547%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20social%20media%20storm%20over%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20child%20rights%20body%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20a%20rape%20threat%20to%20the%20daughter%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-rape-threat-to-abhishek-banerjees-daughter-bengal-child-panel-takes-note-6420547%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kim%20Hye%20Yoon%20surprised%20by%20Byeon%20Woo%20Seok%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1