betterindia.com%2F333887%2Fsangopita-shelter-home-disabled-children-cerebral-palsy-autism-adhd%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20with%20various%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20visual%2C%20intellectual%2C%20hearing%2C%20and%20locomotion%20%E2%80%94%20are%20taught%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laljibhai%20explains.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20programme%20ensures%20that%20these%20students%20are%20included%20in%20the%20mainstream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20inclusive%20schools%20%E2%80%94%20primary%20boys%20school%2C%20primary%20and%20secondary%20girls%20school%2C%20and%20secondary%20and%20higher%20secondary%20co-ed%20school%20%E2%80%94%20provide%20the%20students%20with%20study%20material%20in%20braille%2C%20audio%20content%2C%20and%20facilities%20such%20as%20libraries%2C%20computer%20labs%20with%20a%20screen%20reader%2C%20smart%20classes%2C%20sports%2C%20yoga%20dance%2C%20and%20music%20classes.%20Laljibhai%20adds%20that%20the%20infrastructure%20is%20such%20that%20these%20students%20can%20learn%20in%20the%20mode%20that%20suits%20them%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-4-1723031468.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%20was%20born%20out%20of%20Laljibhai's%20desire%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20elderly%20visually%20impaired%20people%20in%20society%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-4-1723031468.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-4-1723031468-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-4-1723031468-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-ho